-- this project has been abandonned to the high maintenance it needed, and due to Steel dropping Qt as a UI solution.

QSteelWidget is a c++ Qt QWidget sublass that embeds the Steel engine and offers methods to acces its API.

== engine ==
= mouse =
double click toggles engine mode, in which one can move a ghost camera with wasd (+shift and space to move down/up the
y axis relative to the camera).
